Package: sirt
Type: Package
Title: Supplementary Item Response Theory Models
Version: 2.4-17
Date: 2018-01-16 11:01:35
Author: Alexander Robitzsch [aut,cre]
Maintainer: Alexander Robitzsch <robitzsch@ipn.uni-kiel.de>
Description: 
    Supplementary item response theory models to complement existing 
    functions in R, including multidimensional compensatory and
    noncompensatory IRT models, MCMC for hierarchical IRT models and 
    testlet models, NOHARM, Rasch copula model, faceted and 
    hierarchical rater models, ordinal IRT model (ISOP), 
    DETECT statistic, local structural equation modeling (LSEM).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
    CDM (>= 6.0), coda, graphics, lavaan, lavaan.survey, 
    methods, mirt, mvtnorm, Rcpp, sfsmisc, stats, survey, 
    TAM (>= 2.5-5), utils
Suggests:
    gtools, ic.infer, igraph, Matrix, miceadds, pbivnorm, 
    psych, sm
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
URL: https://github.com/alexanderrobitzsch/sirt
License: GPL (>= 2)
